In CSS, this looks something like hsl(60, 70%, 40%).\n\nSUBSCRIBE TO CHANNEL - https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCW5YeuERMmlnqo4oq8vwUpg?sub_confirmation=1\n\n========== CSS for Beginners Playlist ==========\n\nhttps://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL4cUxeGkcC9gQeDH6xYhmO-db2mhoTSrT\n========== HTML Basics Course ==========\n\nhttps://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL4cUxeGkcC9ibZ2TSBaGGNrgh4ZgYE6Cc\n\n========== The Net Ninja ============\n\nFor more front-end development tutorials & to black-belt your coding skills, head over to - https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCW5YeuERMmlnqo4oq8vwUpg or http://thenetninja.co.uk\n\n========== Social Links ==========\n\nTwitter - @TheNetNinja - https://twitter.com/thenetninjauk", 'thumbnails': {'default': {'url': 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/YYMCcm4EM2M/default.jpg', 'width': 120, 'height': 90}, 'medium': {'url': 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/YYMCcm4EM2M/mqdefault.jpg', 'width': 320, 'height': 180}, 'high': {'url': 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/YYMCcm4EM2M/hqdefault.jpg', 'width': 480, 'height': 360}, 'standard': {'url': 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/YYMCcm4EM2M/sddefault.jpg', 'width': 640, 'height': 480}, 'maxres': {'url': 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/YYMCcm4EM2M/maxresdefault.jpg', 'width': 1280, 'height': 720}}, 'channelTitle': 'The Net Ninja', 'playlistId': 'UUW5YeuERMmlnqo4oq8vwUpg', 'position': 1287, 'resourceId': {'kind': 'youtube#video', 'videoId': 'YYMCcm4EM2M'}}}
